summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Lawvek B2B SaaS website. All 11 sections load correctly with proper content, navigation works smoothly, mobile responsiveness is excellent, and premium design elements are implemented perfectly.

Trust Strip with 4 trust signals (AI-assisted review, Licensed lawyer verification, etc.)
Problem section with dark background and 3 numbered problem statements
Approach section with 3 step cards (Complexity Scoring, Right-Sized Workflow, Predictable Pricing)
How It Works section with 5-step visual flow
Benefits section with 6 benefit cards in grid layout
